{"tid":495248,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩帥批評曼城經常用「技術犯規」","createTime":"2017-12-10T13:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T14:02:52.000Z","uid":35928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6eeffcb47d0508f3e365ceea3d3374fc57e1ac79","tid":495248,"uid":35928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:58:12.000Z","msg":"周日曼市打吡大戰前夕，曼聯領隊摩連奴再次開腔，批評曼城球員經常在前場以「技術犯規」阻止對手進攻，似有意向球證施壓。<br />\n<br />\n日前批評曼城球員「有少少風就跌低」的摩帥，再次談及對手踢法︰「他們的戰術是在前場放上大批球員，當失去皮球後便圍著附近範圍，這個轉攻為守的轉換只在數秒內發生，是很高質素。」<br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">但當他們失波後很多時會以『技術犯規』截停球賽，這視乎球證怎樣判罰，這是他的工作，但我不能說關於他的事情</span>。」同時間「寸王」亦耿耿於懷上季交手球證卡頓普的錯誤判決︰「上季比賽教曉我球證的錯誤可以影響球賽，當下半場開始我們落後1︰2時，<span style=\"color: red;\">門將巴禾的犯規應被罰12碼及紅牌離場</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n而對於主將保羅普巴今場停賽，他說︰「我們失去重要的球員，有普巴和沒有普巴的曼聯是很不同，這不是悲觀，只是踢法不同，沒有他我們不會取得上場對阿仙奴的第3個入波，但其他中場可做其他事情，像費蘭尼頭槌出色，馬迪可以遠射，靴里拉亦可有其他貢獻。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=cz0NtoQHsL2naZ4LrITYltZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=6d52f2b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.goal.com/zh-hk/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%91%A9%E5%B8%A5-%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95-%E6%9B%BC%E5%9F%8E-%E7%B6%93%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8-%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%8A%AF%E8%A6%8F/ln9m2kycc5am1now6mcxp8dq7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%2591%25A9%25E5%25B8%25A5-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E6%259B%25BC%25E5%259F%258E-%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E7%258A%25AF%25E8%25A6%258F%2Fln9m2kycc5am1now6mcxp8dq7&d=cz0NtoQHsL2naZ4LrITYltZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=25f96a92\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.goal.com/zh-hk/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%91%A9%E5%B8%A5-%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95-%E6%9B%BC%E5%9F%8E-%E7%B6%93%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8-%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%8A%AF%E8%A6%8F/ln9m2kycc5am1now6mcxp8dq7</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又逼害我獌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"716ee38e9642d6d757414019491e7c0e20658be5","tid":495248,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"NBA整停過鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ef23c5e62c3105b857b7e5cc5f2fae81b7c0c4","tid":495248,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"黑鏝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bea30e73c40ac6d833240cd73ff415404a8655a","tid":495248,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"Nba又然"}]}